description:
&lt;p&gt;The Estates Department is responsible for the repair, maintenance and management of all Building and Engineering Services within the Trust.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Exciting opportunities have arisen for experienced Craftsperson&#39;s (Electrical) to join our multi disciplined Estates Team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holders will be time served and have an electrical background and will be responsible for the provision of engineering maintenance services primarily for the Trust owned buildings within the Teesside locality of the Trust.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Although primarily based at Roseberry Park Hospital, Middlesbrough you may be required to work from other Trust sites for periods of time as the service dictates.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In the event that permanent funding is secured for this post the successful applicant will be confirmed in post on a permanent basis.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Applicants must ensure that prior to applying they have agreement from their current line manager that they can be released on a secondment basis&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;For further details please contact Estates Officers - Neil Richardson on 01642 838120&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
